: decimal;\"><code style=\"word-wrap: break-word; background: none; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; margin: 1em 0px !important; color: rgb(33, 150, 243); border: none !important;\"><span class=\"pun\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(184, 255, 184);\">}</span></code></li></ol></pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"toc_11\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; padding: 8px 15px; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, Tahoma, SimHei, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; background-image: linear-gradient(to right bottom, rgb(0, 188, 212), rgb(63, 81, 181)); background-color: rgb(63, 81, 181); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 3px; border-left: 10px solid rgb(51, 51, 51); text-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 1px 1px 1px; box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 1px 1px 2px;\">函数库</h3>\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">库是函数的集合。将函数定义在文件里并在当前环境中导入那个文件，这样可以创建函数库。</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">假设我们已经在&nbsp;<code style=\"word-wrap: break-word; background: rgb(238, 238, 238); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px 4px; color: rgb(33, 150, 243);\">utils.sh</code>&nbsp;中定义好了所有函数，接着在当前的环境下使用下面的命令导入函数：</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(22, 27, 32); background-image: url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAAICAYAAAA4GpVBAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB90GBgMqHcZ0EYUAAAAZdEVYdENvbW1lbnQAQ3JlYXRlZCB3aXRoIEdJTVBXgQ4XAAAAF0lEQVQI12NgYGAwZsAECDEWBgYGBgYACpwAazfG694AAAAASUVORK5CYII=&quot;); font-size: 14px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 0px 0px 5px; text-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 1px; border-radius: 6px; color: rgb(184, 255, 184); margin: 10px; padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em; white-space: pre-wrap; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1em 2em; padding: 1px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(0, 153, 0); background-image: url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAAICAYAAAA4GpVBAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB90GBgMqHcZ0EYUAAAAZdEVYdENvbW1lbnQAQ3JlYXRlZCB3aXRoIEdJTVBXgQ4XAAAAF0lEQVQI12NgYGAwZsAECDEWBgYGBgYACpwAazfG694AAAAASUVORK5CYII=&quot;); color: rgb(174, 174, 174);\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px; text-indent: -28px; line-height: 2em; list-style-type: decimal;\"><code style=\"word-wrap: break-word; background: none; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px !important; border-radius: 0px !important; margin: 1em 0px !important; color: rgb(33, 150, 243); border: none !important;\"><span class=\"pln\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(184, 255, 184);\">$ source utils</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(184, 255, 184);\">.</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(184, 255, 184);\">sh</span></code></li></ol></pre>\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">之后你就可以像调用其它 Bash 命令那样执行库中任何的函数了。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"toc_12\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; padding: 8px 15px; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, Tahoma, SimHei, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; background-image: linear-gradient(to right bottom, rgb(0, 188, 212), rgb(63, 81, 181)); background-color: rgb(63, 81, 181); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 3px; border-left: 10px solid rgb(51, 51, 51); text-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 1px 1px 1px; box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 1px 1px 2px;\">总结</h3>\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">本文我们讨论了诸多可以提升效率的实用技巧。我希望这篇文章能够启发你去创造自己的技巧。</p>\r\n<hr style=\"word-wrap: break-word; clear: both; margin: 0px 10px; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" />\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">via:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.linuxtechi.com/define-use-functions-linux-shell-script/\" class=\"ext\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 138, 216); text-decoration-line: none; padding: 0px 4px 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">https://www.linuxtechi.com/define-use-functions-linux-shell-script/</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">作者：<a href=\"http://www.linuxtechi.com/author/pradeep/\" class=\"ext\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 138, 216); text-decoration-line: none; padding: 0px 4px 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">Pradeep Kumar</a>&nbsp;选题：<a href=\"https://github.com/lujun9972\" class=\"ext\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 138, 216); text-decoration-line: none; padding: 0px 4px 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">lujun9972</a>&nbsp;译者：<a href=\"https://github.com/LuuMing\" class=\"ext\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 138, 216); text-decoration-line: none; padding: 0px 4px 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">LuuMing</a>&nbsp;校对：<a href=\"https://ganquanzhong.top\">甘全中</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 1.5em 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">本文由&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/LCTT/TranslateProject\" class=\"ext\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 138, 216); text-decoration-line: none; padding: 0px 4px 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">LCTT</a>&nbsp;原创编译，<a href=\"https://linux.cn/article-9954-1.html\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(247, 110, 110); text-decoration-line: none; padding: 0px 4px 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">Linux中国</a>&nbsp;荣誉推出</p>', ' Pradeep Kumar', '甘全中', 'Liunx中国', 0, '2018-08-31 17:33:34', 175, '已审核', '201833310533341.png', 0);
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (184, 16, 'OFweek（第二届）中国人工智能产业大会正式开幕', '<p>&nbsp;<strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Langtinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.25px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">导读：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Langtinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.25px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Langtinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.25px;\">8月30日-31日，由中国高科技行业门户OFweek维科网、HTC高科会主办，OFweek人工智能网承办的&ldquo;OFweek（第二届）中国人工智能产业大会&rdquo;在上海拉开帷幕。</span></p>\r\n<div id=\"articleC\" class=\"article_con\" style=\"padding: 20px 0px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; zoom: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Langtinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, arial, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.25px;\">\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">8月30日－31日，由中国高科技行业门户OFweek维科网、HTC高科会主办，OFweek<span class=\"hrefStyle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://ai.ofweek.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"人工智能\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(146, 3, 70); outline: none;\">人工智能</a></span>网承办的&ldquo;OFweek（第二届）中国人工智能产业大会&rdquo;在上海拉开帷幕。此次会议旨在搭建专为人工智能圈内企业和从业人员交流合作的专业平台，汇集人工智能领域的国际知名企业高层、行业资深专家、专家分析机构等数千位精英，建立业内优势人脉资源，用全新视角透析行业动态，解读在人工智能领域本年度海内外最值得关注的学术与研发进展，1000＋人工智能专业人士共同探讨人工智能难题以及产业落地，提前布局未来大市场。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030139_1535655699091631325.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">此次大会与国内顶尖的人工智能专家深度探讨人工智能芯片、智能传感器、深度学习平台、AI算法、计算机视觉和语音、自然语言处理／理解等<span class=\"hrefStyle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://ai.ofweek.com/CATList-201700-8300-ai.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"人工智能技术\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(146, 3, 70); outline: none;\">人工智能技术</a></span>热点及人工智能在智能硬件、机器人、智慧城市、智能医疗等领域落地实践案例。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030139_1535655699093186456.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">会场现场座无虚席，行业内的企业高层们不远万里来到这里，认真聆听行业专家的分析，共同探讨人工智能难题以及产业落地。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">中国高科技行业门户OFweek维科网CEO、HTC高科会会长李晓阳先生发表开幕式致辞，他表示此次大会将对当前人工智能产业面临的问题进行解答，深入剖析如何推广人工智能技术和如何应用人工智能给社会带来更大的价值。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">此次会议来自香港科技大学机器人学院、国际导航与运动控制科学院、深圳云天励飞、美国高通、Facebook、Video＋＋极链科技、北京旷视、360AI研究院、云知声、中科创达、宇视科技、深兰科技、德国汉堡科学院、图麟信息科技等资深专家与知名企业高管们做出了精彩演讲，对AI行业发展、AI难题以及技术应用进行了剖析和分享，并对维科杯&middot;OFweek 2018（第二届）中国人工智能行业年度评选结果公布并颁奖。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030139_1535655699226356780.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">香港科技大学机器人研究院院长IEEE院士 王煜：人工智能及机器人智能学习</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030139_1535655699960632656.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">香港科技大学研究重点分为四方面：自动化系统与机器人、制造自动化与智慧工厂、人机交互、智慧家庭与智慧城市。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">研究院院长IEEE院士王煜表示他认为目前最有研究价值的是自动驾驶无人车技术，并如何实现安全和更好驾驶而开发的系统。同时透露香港科技大学下一步研究方向重点放在下一代ADAS能够越来越多地利用无线网络连接上，通过使用汽车到汽车和汽车到基础设施的数据来提供更高的价值。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">国际导航与云端控制科学院院士IEEE院士 蔡自兴：人工智能产业化的战略思考</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030140_1535655700752706642.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">蔡自兴院士向我们介绍工智能产业化从历史发展，到新时代人工智能产业化起点高、规模大、质量优、平稳快速并全面发展特点，同时，针对人工智能产业化的8项优先领域智能驾驶与智能网联汽车、智能机器人及服务机器人、智能制造综合系统、计算机视觉与视频图像身份识别系统、自然语言处理与智能翻译系统、智慧医疗与医疗影像辅助诊断系统、智能安防与智慧金融、<span class=\"hrefStyle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://smarthome.ofweek.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"智能家居\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(146, 3, 70); outline: none;\">智能家居</a></span>产品与系统等方面做出详细介绍，并提出人工智能产业化的战略建议以及人工智能产业化的决策案例。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">深圳云天励飞首席方案总监王军：对芯连世界，智创未来进行</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030415_1535655855276956525.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">王军在会上介绍了被誉为全球最大的动态人像系统的云天&ldquo;深目&rdquo;系统，这款被号称是百亿人脸，秒级定位的存在的，一个全球首创&ldquo;云＋端&rdquo;视觉智能技术架构，是如何应用于AI＋新警务、AI＋新治理、AI＋新零售三大方向，并对&ldquo;三驾马车&rdquo;（算法、芯片、数据）如何并驾齐驱做出了深入剖析。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">美国高通公司刘学徽：Qualcomm骁龙移动平台加速终端侧AI</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030415_1535655855302730753.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">高通强调人工智能向终端测的发展，需要依靠用户和设备使得人工智能受到训练、执行和推理。产品市场总监刘学徽表示：&ldquo;智能手机AI体验不能只依靠一个内核，在AI面向图像分类网络时，其准确率与运算次数的对比是基准测试最重要的指标，人工智能软件持续优化，是实现骁龙SoC产品组合性能能在一年内实现两倍提升的重要突破点。&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Facebook大中华区平台合作负责人 濮冠楠：人工智能－规模与创新</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030415_1535655855689618352.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">Facebook是一家软件公司，致力于移动APP开发，目前Facebook日活跃超过22亿人，大中华区平台合作负责人濮冠楠在会上介绍了Facebook在庞大的数据量下如何通过AI技术做到内容审核、质量监控，并共享了开源深度学习工具Torch、人工智能系统WIT．AI、深度学习框架PYTORCH、模块化的深度学习框架caffe2。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Video＋＋极链科技联合创始人＆COO 董慧智：AI新文娱经济的未来空间</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030417_1535655857184139334.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">新文娱是指在互联网赋能下的新型文化娱乐产业，以新的手段实现的娱乐内容或服务。董慧智强调科技创业的动能是人工智能，新文娱产业的动能是视频，而Video＋＋极链科技致力于&ldquo;AI＋文娱&rdquo;的技术落地，Video＋＋正在积累海量结构化视频数据库，并结合用户行为反馈衍生出多维度标签分类在广告、电商以及新商业IP都有着突出的贡献。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">北京旷视科技有限公司副总裁谢亿楠：中国人工智能的系统与准绳</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030417_153565585770420333.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">在目前人工智能产业化领域，副总裁谢亿楠表示AI技术在一年、三年、五年可以实现爆发增长。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">在会上，副总裁谢亿楠向大家分享了AI企业核心资源如何与核心生态系统打通、AI技术、产业升级等方面的解决方法。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">360AI研究院高级技术总监 陈强博士：中国新一代人工智能关键共性技术体系的现状和突破点</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030816_1535656096278647693.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">目前人工智能的四大要素分为场景、算法、算力、数据，而360人工智能业务场景表现在安全、内容两方面。在会上陈强详细为我们介绍了360视频大脑的三大模块：安全（网络安全、线下安全）、IOT智能硬件（360摄像头、360儿童、360车联网）、内容分发（探索、短视频、直播、信息流）。以及如何在目前内容结构化、IOT智能硬件设备数上涨迅猛、4G／5G的普及、互联网内容流量逐渐以视频为主的趋势下，提高短视频分析率、安防监控每日人脸比对次数、端上AR特效平台输出可次数。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">云知声创新事业部总裁陈吉胜：面向AIO的人机交互端芯演进之路</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030816_1535656096073551258.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">&ldquo;2018年5月16日，云知声正式发布首款面向物联网的AI芯片UniOne及解决方案&mdash;&mdash;雨燕（Swift）&rdquo;，陈吉胜表示：&ldquo;AI正在各方面超越人类，人工智能带来的不是增量式的创新，而是颠覆式的新机会。&rdquo;在面向AIoT的人机交互云端芯演进之路上，云知声的目标是助力产业链完成智能化升级。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">在会上陈吉胜向我们介绍了AIoT真正实用落地的关键，必须同时满足的五个要求。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">中科创达副总裁兼智能视觉事业群执行总裁孙力：嵌入式人工智能的挑战与实践</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030816_1535656096228399199.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">中科创达此次从三方面向我们介绍了嵌入式人工智能，嵌入式AI的发展趋势、嵌入式AI的挑战以及如何应用落地、嵌入式AI的一些实践。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">孙力认为AI 服务将在 IoT 场景中无处不在，当前嵌入式 AI 算法计算资源有限，终端处理平台过于碎片化，应用场景和需求过于多样化，性能（准确率－速度）的平衡上如何取舍，生态系统不成熟，功耗与成本较高等方面是嵌入式AI算法应用当前面临的主要问题与挑战。而中科创达未来几年在嵌入式智能视觉的主要工作是在智能视觉上打造一个 灵活可扩展的嵌入式AI平台架构。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">宇视科技<span class=\"hrefStyle\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://ai.ofweek.com/CATList-201700-8200-ai.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"人工智能产品\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(146, 3, 70); outline: none;\">人工智能产品</a></span>线总工程师李聪廷：安防AI应用现状与展望</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831030817_1535656097235764329.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">AI竞争逐步从算法、算力、数据三要素演进为算法、算力、数据、方案、产品、过程六要素。李聪廷表示安防的三次革命是网络化－高清化－智能化的演变，目前，人脸识别成为最热门的AI应用渗透每一个行业，公安、高校、机场、新零售等等。产品线总工程师李聪廷分享了宇视科技如何解决当前人脸识别不完善，存在漏报误报、宽动态低照度、安装不规范、规模落地难、建设成本高、场景定制与个性化需求大等问题。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">深兰科技董事长助理刘凤义博士：人工智能服务民生</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831031019_1535656219385325608.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深兰芯片是一款专用AI 图像处理核心芯片 FPGA 和神经网络语音芯片，运用最先进的视觉模型用于工业化的标准框架，其中DeepblueAI深兰深度强化学习框架是一款自主设计的基于多上下文注意力自适应目标检测框架，是一种适应商业需求的DeepblueAI框架。刘凤义博士分享了深兰做出的AI方案覆盖9大领域（自动驾驶＋整车、零售升级、智能机器人、智慧城市、生物智能、智能语音、安防、芯片、军工／教育等）的应用案例。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">德国汉堡科学院院士张建伟：AI赋能，人机共融</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831031019_1535656219009646312.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">人工智能发展的新动能是高性价比的计算引擎，张建伟表示AI赋能，人机共融助力信息物理系统升级，首先要做的是第一步是将人工智能自动化从生产延伸到社会各个领域，并分享了多模态交互、人机共融机器人的应用以及人工智能发展未来挑战及策略。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">图麟信息科技联合创始人张勋：全面商用化到来，AI全方位融入行业</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831031018_1535656218977997472.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">2018人工智能已经进入全面商用化阶段，张勋表示&ldquo;成熟的技术、政策的支持、海量的市场、丰富的数据以及强大的资本这些多方因素已为人工智能打造了一个&lsquo;沃土&rsquo;，从实验室走向市场，接受市场考验，这是所有企业都将面临的挑战。&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">目前尽管有技术、政策、资本等多层面支撑AI的美好蓝图，但对于AI创业者而言，终究都要回归到商业本质。图麟科技认为商用化就是衡量人工智能企业是否具备价值的重要考量。张勋在会上分享了如何以原创算法为核心推动AI全面商用化的完整解决方案。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">维科杯&middot;OFweek 2018（第二届）中国人工智能行业年度评选颁奖典礼</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">人工智能评选活动已历经了近半年的时间筹备，得到行业协会、媒体、业内人士及社会各界的高度关注。超过100家人工智能行业上下游厂商踊跃自主或推荐报名参评，在移动端微信投票平台，超过10万次的有效投票，本次大会公布了人工智能行业年度的4大奖项，其中共有37家企业获奖，这些获奖企业分别是：</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">&middot;OFweek 2018&ldquo;维科杯&rdquo;中国人工智能行业优秀产品应用奖</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">科大讯飞股份有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">浙江宇视科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">科沃斯商用机器人有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深兰科技（上海）有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">北京佳光科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳市普渡科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳云天励飞技术有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳市优必选科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳新物种科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">北京视连通科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831031019_1535656219894798844.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline: none; max-width: 85%; height: auto !important;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">&middot;OFweek2018&ldquo;维科杯&rdquo;中国人工智能技术创新奖</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">重庆爱奇艺智能科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳奥比中光科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">北京物灵智能科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">速感科技（北京）有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳勇艺达机器人有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">中科创达软件股份有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">深圳市速腾聚创科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">苏州科达科技股份有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">上海极链网络科技有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word;\">数据堂（北京）科技股份有限公司</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; word-break: break-word; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://images.ofweek.com/Upload/News/2018-8/31/guolei/20180831031020_1535656220396294835.png\" width=\"600\" style=\"padding: 0