p;c=civilnews&amp;pn=8\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">三个最高级别工作组如何运转？</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; height: 27px; line-height: 27px; background: url(&quot;//gss0.bdstatic.com/5foIcy0a2gI2n2jgoY3K/static/fisp_static/news/img/top_bg_f32315c.png&quot;) left -270px no-repeat; overflow: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://3w.huanqiu.com/a/0c789f/7G50kCcHblm?agt=8\" mon=\"ct=0&amp;a=2&amp;c=civilnews&amp;pn=9\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">印象旅游骗局：数千景点免费游为假，疑为传销卖卡</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; height: 27px; line-height: 27px; background: url(&quot;//gss0.bdstatic.com/5foIcy0a2gI2n2jgoY3K/static/fisp_static/news/img/top_bg_f32315c.png&quot;) left -270px no-repeat; overflow: hidden;\"><a href=\"http://news.ifeng.com/a/20180910/60044292_0.shtml?_zbs_baidu_news\" mon=\"ct=0&amp;a=2&amp;c=civilnews&amp;pn=10\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">妇女报谈&ldquo;娘炮&rdquo;争议：尊重审美多元 反对恶俗炒作</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; height: 27px; line-height: 27px; background: url(&quot;//gss0.bdstatic.com/5foIcy0a2gI2n2jgoY3K/static/fisp_static/news/img/top_bg_f32315c.png&quot;) left -270px no-repeat; overflow: hidden;\"><a href=\"http://news.ifeng.com/a/20180910/60044675_0.shtml\" mon=\"ct=0&amp;a=2&amp;c=civilnews&amp;pn=11\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">台湾省有些着急&ldquo;可以理解&rdquo;，但美国更着急真是&ldquo;惟恐..</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; height: 27px; line-height: 27px; background: url(&quot;//gss0.bdstatic.com/5foIcy0a2gI2n2jgoY3K/static/fisp_static/news/img/top_bg_f32315c.png&quot;) left -270px no-repeat; overflow: hidden;\"><a href=\"http://news.ifeng.com/a/20180910/60044659_0.shtml?_zbs_baidu_news\" mon=\"ct=0&amp;a=2&amp;c=civilnews&amp;pn=12\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">柯文哲被曝20日将南下探望陈水扁</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"l-middle-col\" alog-group=\"log-civil-middle\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; float: left; width: 240px; font-family: arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti;\">\r\n<div class=\"mod\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<div class=\"hd\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 6px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 24px; line-height: 24px; text-align: right; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: rgb(37, 66, 130); border-image: initial; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; float: left; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(37, 66, 130); background-image: initial; b